    <br/>
    The sign STRONG is related to the concepts of: brave, courageous, heal, 
healthy, robust, fit, and well.
    <br/>
    The difference between all these concepts and the concept of
"strong" is that STRONG starts with "fist" handshapes
whereas the other concepts tend to start with "relaxed five" handshapes.
